Problem Statement : 
	Write a Java program to create an integer array by taking length as input from the user.
	Take the contents of the array from the user and store the contents in the array. 
	Display the contents of the array on to the Console.
	
Explanation : 
	We will take the user input as the length of the array. Reading the elements and Storing them in 
	the index by using the loop. And Displaying the content of the array by using the For loop.